    v2 = 1.0

    tmp = (0.33 * wp.cos((v1 + 0.18 * tmp + 0.17)))
    v1 = wp.abs(v2)
    v1 = ((0.09 * (v1 + 0.62 - tmp + 0.65)) + wp.sin(0.84))
    tmp = (0.52 * ((tmp + 0.70 + v0 + 0.26) * (v2 + 0.71 - v0 + 0.04)))
    v2 = (0.33 / wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.36)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
